item.title: AX 2012 R3 CU8 CU9 and TFS Online 2013 Error
item.author: luan52@outlook.com (Hi there, this is Max Nguyen)
item.description: Fix TFS connectivity issues in Dynamics AX 2012 R3 CU8/CU9 with TFS Online 2013. Solution requires installing Team Foundation Server 2010 SP1 Object Model and hotfix KB2662296.
